Furthermore, we built an integrated model for OS of DLBCL patients with six factors, comprising age at diagnosis, stage, extra nodal sites number, the ECOG performance score, drug resistance probability of doxorubicin and drug resistance probability of vincristine. The prediction score was calculated according the following formula:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
